{"tid":1885004,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"原來歷史上係有西京出現","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T07:04:23.000Z","uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f388149e228ec9e8bec4b229473cd44ed2c561b3","tid":1885004,"uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"公元918年，高麗王朝在松岳（今開城）建國，926年定平壤為「西京」。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b4ed1354e225adae5a954a2f32ccace8a4e318","tid":1885004,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"比唐三藏取經啦"},{"pid":"903dc43981d2b08a57b3c9e5d07ffea6185394b4","tid":1885004,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"西京魚？"},{"pid":"766a25945e46bc0d6397d17373b7dbf250d7089a","tid":1885004,"uid":293557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"唐朝同日本都有西京啦, 個個國家國都凡係搞過東遷或者同時有幾個都城都有啦"},{"pid":"13e54ddbbbae103062853120f3f947f40b268cca","tid":1885004,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"中京都有"},{"pid":"1c64a86f6d7c846ed8f21de83a5a4dc5671af97c","tid":1885004,"uid":29130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"西京燒，是以西京漬醃魚肉後再直接燒的料理，當中的醬汁以白味噌做底，可加酒、味醂等調味，混成西京漬，味道帶甜。為了保留傳統特色，是次的西京漬只用了西京味噌、清酒、味醂和糖。西京味噌加入清酒後令味噌的香氣更明顯，準備時已經令人垂涎三尺。如果不想自己混醃料的話，日式超市亦有這個醃醬出售，塗上後醃一晚便可。"},{"pid":"f871f575680b81dc07dc66c2d8a0a5186ea645ae","tid":1885004,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"最衰都係唐僧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3470e07f10c043fb318785dbf586328c455cd63","tid":1885004,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"可以當成都係西京"},{"pid":"d8bd2e6c1784adbbb4387407a5fc34040d53efc8","tid":1885004,"uid":300694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"西安，古稱長安，漢、唐曾建都於此，真正的西京。"},{"pid":"0391fdbc7a7df111b3ff63e40b97993239c4759c","tid":1885004,"uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13e54ddbbbae103062853120f3f947f40b268cca","tid":1885004,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"中京都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"名古屋"},{"pid":"dbb4b696faf2ea5c912e131e24316af5531af17a","tid":1885004,"uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13e54ddbbbae103062853120f3f947f40b268cca","tid":1885004,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"中京都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:26:06.000Z","msg":"得西京而家唔存在"},{"pid":"28044941e20d0e3c67103b1dbf2261926ddbfb79","tid":1885004,"uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f388149e228ec9e8bec4b229473cd44ed2c561b3","tid":1885004,"uid":312846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"公元918年，高麗王朝在松岳（今開城）建國，926年定平壤為「西京」。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"應該係朝鮮先啱<br />\n古代無分南北"},{"pid":"760c1573bea0030321180aa1b62c34ea0ebb6ed5","tid":1885004,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"香港嘅西京係屯門定荃灣？"},{"pid":"8eb50999880dcf5bcbc5ac8c426554e13485d2a7","tid":1885004,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"760c1573bea0030321180aa1b62c34ea0ebb6ed5","tid":1885004,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"香港嘅西京係屯門定荃灣？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"香港既北京係西環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3138f309ec8da751aa29e7eb268fbb13bb1384f6","tid":1